  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThe section goes **blank** if we scroll up or down in any scrollable area such as 1:1 chats, settings, and any channels.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Open the Status Desktop app\r\n2. Navigate to any scroll-enabled section (Eg: 1:1 chat, Settings, and any channel under any community)\r\n3. Scroll up or down\r\n\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2022-12-12 at 4 40 10 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19339952/207031231-da5e3161-5370-45c9-ae7e-ab6a0a38603d.png)\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2022-12-12 at 8 29 53 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19339952/207078364-d66688d6-7e56-44ef-a0dd-be67b8a71d58.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nThe user can scroll up or down without the section going blank.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: `v0.8.0`\r\n- Operating System: `macOS 13.0.1`\r\n- Mouse: `Logitech Master MX 3`\r\n\r\n",
